            "text": "<h3><strong>Ergonomic Design & Angle</strong></h3><ul><li>Unique <strong>27° optimized incline</strong> designed to support natural body positioning<br/></li><li>Ergonomic <strong>wedge shaped design</strong> for stable, balanced support<br/></li><li>Helps maintain a comfortable angle without slipping or collapsing<br/></li></ul><h3><strong>Foam & Support</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>High density memory foam core</strong> for firm yet comfortable support<br/></li><li>Contours to the body while maintaining its shape<br/></li><li>Designed to resist sagging, even with repeated use<br/></li></ul><h3><strong>Comfort & Materials</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Premium soft touch cover</strong>, breathable and skin-friendly<br/></li><li><strong>Removable, machine washable cover</strong> for easy care<br/></li><li><strong>Non-slip base</strong> to keep the pillow securely in place<br/></li></ul><h3><strong>Design & Practical Details</strong></h3><ul><li>Discreet, modern design that blends easily into any bedroom<br/></li><li><strong>Integrated side handles</strong> for easy repositioning<br/></li><li>Carefully sized to provide support without being bulky<br/></li></ul><h3><strong>Versatility & Use</strong></h3><ul><li>Suitable for lying or semi-seated positions<br/></li><li>Can be used as a <strong>back, waist, or hip support pillow</strong><br/></li><li>Ideal for relaxation, comfort, and positioning support<br/></li><li>Suitable for different body types<br/></li></ul><h3><strong>Quality & Safety</strong></h3><ul><li>Made from <strong>non toxic, durable materials</strong><br/></li><li>Designed for <strong>long lasting comfort and structural stability</strong><br/></li><li>Comfort product – <strong>non-medical use</strong></li></ul>",
